      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "### Release Notes for Version 2.3.1\n\n**Login Experience Improved**\nWe've ironed out a pesky bug that previously caused your login redirect to act up. Now, rest assured that you'll be smoothly redirected after logging in, making your experience seamless and hassle-free.\n\n**Faster API Calls**\nOur API endpoint timeout has been extended from 30 seconds to a more generous 60 seconds. This means faster, more reliable responses, allowing you to work smarter and get more done in less time.\n\n**Mobile Dashboard Enhanced**\nSay goodbye to the frustration of overflowing content on your mobile dashboard. We've patched a CSS overflow issue, ensuring that you can access all the information you need without any hiccups, no matter what device you're using.\n\n**Efficient User Profile Searches**\nWe've optimized our database queries for user profile searches, making them faster and more efficient. Now, when you search for your profile or others', you'll notice quicker results, saving you precious time and improving your overall experience.",
